   CODEBREAKERS (San Francisco) _ Two Israeli researchers say they
have found an efficient way to crack the encryption scheme that
protects the privacy of conversations and data transmissions over a
type of wireless phone used by more than 215 million people
worldwide. By Sara Robinson.
</P>
<P>
   EXXON-MOBI (Undated) _ Exxon Mobil Corp., which was created last
week after Exxon completed its acquisition of Mobil, has revoked a
Mobil policy that provided health-care coverage to the partners of
newly hired gay employees. By Richard A. Oppel Jr.
