<P>
   FORECAST-AD-COLUMN (New York) _ How upbeat are the two leading
forecasters of advertising spending about the prospects for the
marketing and media industries in 2000? On Monday, they almost
warbled in unison a medley of ``Blue Skies'' and ``Cockeyed
Optimist'' in outlining their predictions for strong, sustained
growth. By Stuart Elliott.
