   MRSCLINTON-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ Michiko Kakutani reviews
``Hillary's Choice,'' by Gail Sheehy (Random House).
</P>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY (Moved in ``k'' category)  &LR;
</P>
