<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-07 14:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1691 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u t BC-TRAVEL-QUEENSLAND-BOS     12-07 1102
