<DOCNO> NYT19991207.0095 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-07 14:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1719 &Cx1f; tad-z
u p BC-CAMPAIGN-COST08-COX     12-07 1095
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CAMPAIGN-COST08-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    GORE, FIRST LADY FREQUENT FLYER MILES BILLED TO TAXPAYERS
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
 &HT;    By JULIA MALONE
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
