Floridians play the Florida Lottery, how much they gamble and what
games they play vary widely. For most middle-class and well-to-do
Floridians, lottery means Lotto, the agency's flagship game that
dangles millions, even tens of millions, as a possible reward for a
$1 bet. (Date, Palm Beach Post). 12. WITH GRAPHIC.
