doesn't survive on luck alone. Sophisticated marketing make up the
backbone of the Florida Lottery's efforts that each day, seven days
a week, 365 days a year, spends an average $99,000 encouraging
Floridians to gamble. (Date, Palm Beach Post). 49. WITH GRAPHIC.
