<P>
   CHINA-WOMEN (Jiangyong, China) _ For thousands of years, women
in remote southern China have shared a secret. Denied a formal
education, socially and intellectually isolated, they devised a
language to use after they were separated by marriage. Now only a
handful are left who still know it. By Indira A.R. Lakshmanan. 1400
words.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
