<DOCNO> NYT19991207.0192 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-07 18:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
