<SLUG> BC-FINFRONTS-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   (mk) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   FOR WEDNESDAY AMs
</P>
<P>
   Business Day Front Page
</P>
<P>
   (All stories will be coded ``f'' unless otherwise noted)
</P>
<P>
   (Lede)
</P>
<P>
   HASBRO-CUTS (Undated) _ Hasbro Inc., the maker of Furby, Star
Wars and Pokemon toys, said on Tuesday that it would slash 2,200
jobs in a sweeping restructuring to take advantage of growing
demand for electronic toys. By Milt Freudenheim.
</P>
