the lighting of Hanukah candles in Barak's office on Tuesday.
Israel said on Tuesday it would not launch new settlement projects
before a final peace treaty is signed, but the Palestinians said
the promise was not enough to bring them back to the negotiating
table. The crisis erupted just as Secretary of State Madeleine
Albright arrived in the Middle East to check progress in
negotiations on a final peace treaty. (Rina Castelnuovo/The New
