make sure you can play equally well to your personal and
professional life,'' writes Smith, who is also the father of
15-year-old Lindsey and 11-year-old Roland. ``I'm going to be
missing meetings occasionally because of my kids' audition or
performance.'' (Cynthia Howe/The New York Times)
